### Deployment Checklist

**When using `--deploy` command:**
- ✅ Regression tests run automatically
- ✅ All tests must pass (0 failures)
- ✅ Build with 0 errors, 0 warnings
- ✅ NuGet deployed automatically
- ✅ Git commit+push automatic
- ✅ One command does everything

**Manual deployment (not recommended):**
- [ ] Run `--regressiontest` command (all 5 test suites)
- [ ] All tests must pass (0 failures)
- [ ] Build with 0 errors, 0 warnings
- [ ] Update PROJECT_STATUS.md with version
- [ ] Review changes in git diff
- [ ] Deploy via Azure-NugetVersionPush.ps1
- [ ] Git commit and push manually

**If ANY test fails:**
- ❌ DO NOT deploy
- 🔍 Investigate and fix the failure
- ✅ Re-run all tests
- ✅ Only deploy when all tests pass

### Quick Test Command

```powershell
# Run all regression tests
Write-Host "Running Regression Tests..." -ForegroundColor Cyan
$results = @()

$results += dotnet run --project c:\opt\src\DedgeCommon\DedgeCommonVerifyFkDatabaseHandler\VerifyFunctionality.csproj
$results += dotnet run --project c:\opt\src\DedgeCommon\TestWorkObject\TestWorkObject.csproj
$results += pwsh -File "C:\opt\src\DedgePsh\_Modules\GlobalFunctions\Test-WorkObjectExport.ps1"
$results += dotnet run --project c:\opt\src\DedgeCommon\TestNotification\TestNotification.csproj
$results += dotnet test c:\opt\src\DedgeCommon\TestGlobalSettings\TestGlobalSettings.csproj

if ($results -contains 1) {
    Write-Host "❌ REGRESSION TESTS FAILED - DO NOT DEPLOY" -ForegroundColor Red
    exit 1
} else {
    Write-Host "✅ ALL REGRESSION TESTS PASSED - OK TO DEPLOY" -ForegroundColor Green
    exit 0
}
```

