## 🎯 Common Tasks

### Add New Database Provider
1. Create handler class implementing `IDbHandler`
2. Add enum value to `DedgeConnection.DatabaseProvider`
3. Update `DedgeConnection.GenerateConnectionString()`
4. Update `DedgeDbHandler.Create()` factory methods
5. Add connection logging (use `DedgeNLog.Trace`)
6. Update README.md with provider information

### Add New Feature
1. Implement feature in appropriate class
2. Add XML documentation comments
3. Update `DedgeCommon/README.md`
4. Add tests if applicable
5. Update version (Minor for new features)
6. Deploy to feed

### Fix Bug
1. Identify and fix issue
2. Add/update tests
3. Update version (Patch for bug fixes)
4. Deploy to feed

